<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #16a34a;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
    }
    .product-info {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .review-content {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #f0f9ff;
      border-left: 4px solid #16a34a;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #16a34a;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Your Review Has Been Approved!</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello <%= @user.username || @user.email %>,</p>
    
    <p>Great news! Your review for <strong><%= @product.name %></strong> has been approved and is now visible to other customers.</p>
    
    <div class="product-info">
      <h3>Product: <%= @product.name %></h3>
      <p>Your rating: <%= @review.rating %>/5</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="review-content">
      <p><em>"<%= @review.comment %>"</em></p>
    </div>
    
    <p>Thank you for taking the time to share your experience with our community. Your feedback helps other customers make informed decisions.</p>
    
    <a href="<%= product_url(@product) %>" class="button">View Your Review</a>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent from Super Ghana App. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
      <p>&copy; <%= Date.today.year %> Super Ghana App. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
